<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hide&nbsp;system&nbsp;log&nbsp;data</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p><tt>MANU-13 COMMUNICATIONS LOG</tt></p>
<p><tt>DATE: 2150-03-04</tt></p>
<p><tt>TIME: 08:46:37 UST</tt></p>
<p><tt>UNKNOWN has connected to MANU-13 (text-only).</tt></p>
